def correction(dataset,thershold):
    corr_matrix=set()
    corr_col=df.corr()
    for i in range(len(corr_col.columns)):
        for j in range(i):
            if corr_col.iloc[i,j]>thershold:
                colName=corr_col.columns[i]
                corr_matrix.add(colName)
    return corr_matrix
